sequenceDiagram
    participant AI as AI Agent
    participant Bus as Agent Bus

    Note over AI,Bus: === AI 自发现流程 ===

    Note over AI: 人类给 AI 一个 URL
    Note over AI: http://agent-bus.company.com

    AI->>Bus: GET /
    Bus-->>AI: service: Agent Bus
    Bus-->>AI: installation: uv add requests
    Bus-->>AI: registration: method, endpoint, body_example
    Bus-->>AI: authentication: headers
    Bus-->>AI: capabilities: [...]
    Bus-->>AI: sdk_url: /sdk

    AI->>AI: 执行: uv add requests

    AI->>Bus: GET /sdk
    Bus-->>AI: code: class AgentBusClient...

    AI->>AI: 保存为 agent_bus_sdk.py

    AI->>Bus: POST /register
    Note right of AI: name: ai-coder-001
    Note right of AI: capabilities: [code, debug]
    Bus-->>AI: agent_id, token, card

    AI->>AI: 初始化 client
    AI->>AI: self.agent_id = agent_id
    AI->>AI: self.token = token

    loop 每 30s
        AI->>Bus: client.inbox(since)
        Bus-->>AI: [messages]
        AI->>AI: LLM 处理每条消息
    end
